  <PropertyA>@(SomeItemGroup)</PropertyA>
  <PropertyB>$(PropertyA)</PropertyB>

<Message Importance="high" Text="$(PropertyA)"/>

  <PropertyA>@(SomeItemGroup->'%(SomeItem)', '')</PropertyA> => One String for List
